551
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,960
"How happy I feel at this sight!"

552
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:37,510
"I croon this poem in delight."

553
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:39,270
Well done!

554
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:46,440
