658
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,550
when they are in my office.

659
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:56,720
That's clever.

660
00:33:59,160 --> 00:34:00,240
By the way,

661
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:00,960
