709
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:17,150
Don't believe him.

710
00:36:18,190 --> 00:36:19,630
Why does it sound real to me?

711
00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:21,920
Mr. Zhang,

712
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:22,920
