718
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,510
Okay, Mr. Zhang.

719
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:33,070
Bye.

720
00:36:37,630 --> 00:36:39,840
These people are too greedy.

721
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,800
I can't believe

722
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,510
